body_html:
I figured it out, it's my processor. From what I recall, TensorFlow started compiling versions after r1.5 to use AVX support. However, my server's processor (Intel X5675) doesn't have AVX support.

I was looking to perform some upgrades to my server anyway, guess the processors need to be first for this project. I'll go ahead with closing this out as this is a hardware issue, and not software.
